The clothes didn't cling to her body.
There were lots of people.

1025
01:30:22,668 --> 01:30:24,751
I hadn't thought about them.

1026
01:30:25,501 --> 01:30:28,126
There are witnesses everywhere.

1027
01:30:47,168 --> 01:30:48,626
OCTOBER 22, 1962

1028
01:30:48,876 --> 01:30:49,960
KENNEDY SPEAKS

1029
01:30:50,168 --> 01:30:52,751
<i>Additional sites, not yet completed,</i>

1030
01:30:53,001 --> 01:30:53,960
<i>appear to be designed</i>

1031
01:30:54,168 --> 01:30:56,793
<i>for intermediate range
ballistic missiles,</i>

1032
01:30:57,001 --> 01:31:01,543
<i>capable of striking most of the major
cities in the Western Hemisphere,</i>

1033
01:31:01,793 --> 01:31:04,835
<i>ranging as far north
as Hudson Bay, Canada,</i>

1034
01:31:05,585 --> 01:31:07,543
<i>and as far south as Lima, Peru.</i>

1035
01:31:07,960 --> 01:31:09,835
<i>In addition, jet bombers</i>

1036
01:31:10,085 --> 01:31:12,835
<i>capable of carrying nuclear weapons</i>

1037
01:31:13,085 --> 01:31:15,543
<i>are now being uncrated
and assembled in Cuba</i>

1038
01:31:16,585 --> 01:31:19,835
<i>while the necessary air bases
are being prepared.</i>

1039
01:31:20,085 --> 01:31:23,210
<i>To halt this offensive buildup,
a strict quarantine</i>

1040
01:31:23,418 --> 01:31:28,251
<i>on all military equipment under
shipment to Cuba is being initiated.</i>

1041
01:31:28,501 --> 01:31:31,960
<i>Should these offensive
military preparations continue,</i>

1042
01:31:32,293 --> 01:31:34,751
<i>thus increasing
the threat to the Hemisphere,</i>

1043
01:31:34,960 --> 01:31:37,460
<i>further action will be justified.</i>

1044
01:31:37,668 --> 01:31:41,460
<i>I have directed the Armed Forces
to prepare for any eventualities.</i>

1045
01:31:47,876 --> 01:31:49,043
Nothing makes sense.

1046
01:31:50,168 --> 01:31:52,751
People move and talk
as if war were a game.

1047
01:32:10,585 --> 01:32:12,126
What if it began right now?

1048
01:32:16,001 --> 01:32:17,751
Protesting is useless.

1049
01:32:18,001 --> 01:32:19,751
I'll die just like the others.

1050
01:32:21,085 --> 01:32:22,751
This island is a trap.

1051
01:32:24,293 --> 01:32:26,751
We're too small, too poor.

1052
01:32:27,585 --> 01:32:29,251
It's a very expensive dignity.

1053
01:32:29,501 --> 01:32:36,126
We decidedly reject
any attempt at supervision,

1054
01:32:37,001 --> 01:32:39,751
any attempt at inspection
of our country.

1055
01:32:39,960 --> 01:32:41,918
Our country will not be subjected
to inspection.

1056
01:32:43,001 --> 01:32:44,960
We are the ones who run this country,

1057
01:32:45,168 --> 01:32:49,960
and we know how we can defend
our integrity, our sovereignty.

1058
01:32:50,585 --> 01:32:55,960
They threaten us with being
the target of nuclear attacks.

1059
01:32:56,793 --> 01:32:58,460
They don't frighten us.

1060
01:32:59,251 --> 01:33:02,460
We must know how to live
in the era we find ourselves in

1061
01:33:02,668 --> 01:33:05,251
with the dignity
with which we should live.

1062
01:33:05,793 --> 01:33:08,335
All of us, men, women,

1063
01:33:09,376 --> 01:33:10,751
young and old,

1064
01:33:11,376 --> 01:33:15,043
we are all united
in this time of danger,

1065
01:33:16,001 --> 01:33:20,543
and ours, the fate of all
the revolutionaries and the patriots,

1066
01:33:21,376 --> 01:33:23,960
will be the same fate,

1067
01:33:24,585 --> 01:33:27,751
and the victory will belong to us all.

1068
01:33:28,001 --> 01:33:30,043
Homeland or death,
we shall overcome!

1069
